# Rules: if an adjudicated entry's key OR any alias exists in v2, the
# entry BODY is replaced but the EXISTING key is preserved (so \cite
# commands stay valid). Otherwise the entry is appended under its
# canonical key. Any key containing 'loveland' is PURGED (M1) and
# subramonian2024degreebias is appended. v2 is never modified.
# CPU-only, ~10 seconds. Paste the full printed report back.
